  "description": "A close-up, vibrant shot focusing on the interior of a red tulip. The petals are a soft, slightly muted red, curving and folding in a symmetrical pattern. At the center is the flower's reproductive structure: dark purple/black anthers surrounding a bright yellow pistil. The anthers appear dusted with pollen. Light filters through the petals, creating subtle shadows and highlights that emphasize their texture. A blurred green background suggests foliage.",
